---
title: "LLM调用完整时序图（含预算检查 + finish_reason校验）"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as TMS Agent
    participant Budget as TokenBudget
    participant Factory as ProviderFactory
    participant Provider as LLMProvider<br/>(DeepSeek/Qwen)
    participant LLM as LLM API
    participant Ledger as TokenLedger
    participant Fallback as 规则引擎

    Agent->>Budget: pre_check(estimated_tokens)
    alt 预算不足
        Budget-->>Agent: ❌ BudgetExceededError
        Agent->>Agent: 触发紧急通知，拒绝任务
    else 预算充足
        Budget-->>Agent: ✅ 允许继续

        Agent->>Factory: get(model_name)
        Factory-->>Agent: LLMProvider实例

        Agent->>Provider: chat_completion(LLMRequest)
        Provider->>Provider: 构建 messages（System+History+Query+Tools）

        Provider->>LLM: HTTP POST /chat/completions
        LLM-->>Provider: 原始HTTP响应

        Provider->>Provider: 解析响应
        Provider->>Provider: 校验 finish_reason

        alt finish_reason = "stop" 或 "tool_calls"
            Provider-->>Agent: ✅ LLMResponse(content, usage, finish_reason)
            Agent->>Budget: charge(usage)
            Agent->>Ledger: record(request_id, model, usage, finish_reason)
            Ledger-->>Agent: ✅ 记录完成
            Agent->>Agent: 正常处理响应

        else finish_reason = "length"
            Provider-->>Agent: ❌ TruncationError (NonRetryable)
            Agent->>Fallback: execute_rule(device_id, error_code)
            Fallback-->>Agent: 确定性规则建议
            Agent->>Ledger: record(request_id, "truncation", usage)
            Agent->>Agent: 标记任务为 FALLBACK_RULE_APPLIED

        else finish_reason = "content_filter"
            Provider-->>Agent: ⚠️ ContentFilterError (NonRetryable)
            Agent->>Ledger: record(request_id, "content_filter", usage)
            Agent->>Agent: 返回安全拒绝提示

        else HTTP 429 / 5xx
            Provider-->>Agent: ❌ RetryableError
            loop 指数退避重试（最多3次）
                Agent->>Provider: chat_completion(同一请求)
                Provider->>LLM: 重试HTTP请求
                LLM-->>Provider: 响应
            end
            alt 重试成功
                Provider-->>Agent: ✅ LLMResponse
            else 重试耗尽
                Provider-->>Agent: ❌ ProviderUnavailableError
                Agent->>Factory: get(fallback_model)
                note over Agent,Factory: 切换到备用模型（Qwen/通义）
            end
        end
    end
